Class WellBeingTipsController

java.lang.Object
com.cab302.wellbeing.controller.WellBeingTipsController
public class WellBeingTipsController extends Object
This class is a controller for the WellBeing Tips functionality in the application. It provides methods to handle button clicks and switch scenes.
